// SQLite for dev/VPS; schema 保持 Postgres 相容(切換只改 provider + url)
// SQLite 不支援 enum,category 用 String,值域由 lib/works.ts 的 CATEGORIES 驗證

generator client {
  provider = "prisma-client-js"
}

datasource db {
  provider = "sqlite"
  url      = env("DATABASE_URL")
}

model Work {
  id          String   @id @default(cuid())
  slug        String   @unique
  title       String
  category    String // MUSIC_VIDEO | COMMERCIAL | CG_FILM | EXPERIMENT
  description String   @default("")
  client      String?
  role        String?
  software    String   @default("")
  year        Int
  aspect      String   @default("16:9") // 16:9 | 9:16 | 1:1 | 4:5,排版依據
  coverImage  String   @default("")
  coverBlur   String?
  previewClip String?
  videoUrl    String?
  externalUrl String?
  stills      Still[]
  featured    Boolean  @default(false)
  published   Boolean  @default(false)
  sortOrder   Int      @default(0)
  createdAt   DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt   DateTime @updatedAt
}

model Still {
  id        String @id @default(cuid())
  url       String
  blur      String?
  sortOrder Int    @default(0)
  work      Work   @relation(fields: [workId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  workId    String
}

model Settings {
  id             Int     @id @default(1)
  siteName       String  @default("BOB")
  tagline        String  @default("CG Director / Motion Designer")
  location       String  @default("Taipei, Taiwan")
  showreelUrl    String?
  showreelPoster String?
  aboutText      String  @default("")
  email          String  @default("")
  instagram      String?
  vimeo          String?
  behance        String?
}
